                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d288">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Morgan</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Seward</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <note rend="inline" type="source">[Extract.]</note>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 66.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">United States Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="italic">Lisbon</hi>,</placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1861-04-06">
                            <hi rend="italic">April</hi> 6, 1861</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: * * * * * * * * *</p>
                <p>During the evening his Majesty inquired with interest as to the condition of
                    affairs in the United States, but when I assured him, as I had before done on a
                    similar occasion, that the Union would be preserved, his manner was more
                    expressive of doubt than belief, though he replied that he hoped I was not
                    mistaken, as it would be a great pity to see so fine a country ruined, and I
                    regret to say that my colleagues, and European politicians generally, regard the
                    disruption of the States as an established fact.</p>
                <p rend="center">* * * * * * * *</p>
                <p>With high respect, I have the honor to be your obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>GEORGE W. MORGAN.</signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. W. H. <hi rend="smallcaps">Seward</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Secretary of
                            State</hi>.</p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
